  "prompt": "Where can I download the TVF's Humorously Yours theme song?",
  "response": "To download the theme song of TVF's \"Humorously Yours,\" you can try the following options:\n\n1. **YouTube:** Often, theme songs for TV shows are uploaded by the creators or fans on YouTube. You can search for the theme song on YouTube and use any reliable online YouTube to MP3 converter to download the audio.\n\n2. **Streaming Services:** Music streaming platforms like Spotify, Apple Music, or Amazon Music might have the theme song available, either in a TV soundtrack or single format. If available, you can download it for offline listening if you have a subscription to these services.\n\n3. **Official Website or Social Media:** Check TVF's official website or their social media accounts. Sometimes creators upload tracks for promotional purposes, and they might provide direct download links or more information on where you can get the song.\n\n4. **Third-party download sites:** Be cautious when using third-party sites for downloading music, as they might host pirated content or unsafe files. Always try to use legitimate sources where possible.\n\nIf you can\u2019t find the theme song through these avenues, you might consider reaching out to TVF directly through their contact page or social media to inquire if they have any official sources for downloading the song.",
